{"tid":1391703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論】發揮香港人的優勢，應如何最大程度利用手上的遊戲幣！","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:24:57.000Z","uid":274336,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ed751c5f373cd25714d30edfa0e5f3d65492e66c","tid":1391703,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:51:58.000Z","msg":"以下作一個開放討論，應該點樣每個人可以利用自己的優勢去參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 有經濟收入能力的工作型NPC</span><br />\n可以印製大量傳單擺在各區的連儂墻，讓人幫手派。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 有時間和精力的宣傳小精靈</span><br />\n去到連儂墻可以攞傳單發散去每一個小區派，深入地做文宣宣傳工作。提高所有支持者的參與率，同時持續地轉化不支持的人去了解，最後支持我哋。<br />\n（其實派傳單落信箱是否可行？）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有見兩日前，大家瘋狂討論前線有冇飽飯食。大家都可以關注一下，做宣傳工作的巴絲和手足們對於印製傳單或banner，在經濟能力上係咪會有負擔。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家下面留言解放更多npc角色，討論比意見。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />遊戲幣要攞黎用架，我想用但係冇咩渠道和想法，歡迎各位巴絲留下安全的渠道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254394b0393be580790a3d3c66164a962019fe56","tid":1391703,"uid":187755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:53:29.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"30fa5935a34355b01eee5345a9a637beb75b671b","tid":1391703,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"咁長時間以嚟，大家的想法和執行力都非常地高，不過好似近期唔係太多人開討論方案的Post，希望拋磚引玉一下，引導下大家發散思維。如果有一個好方案，相信大家都會落力支持，只係好多人其實唔知應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec2ec4b7cc7a5413ac86ab749b91abea9c36210","tid":1391703,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:56:19.000Z","msg":"香港加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390913</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9b43a2923d07608e0246ac89bdf7077ba959b893","tid":1391703,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"之前睇完遊戲傳單，都會順手塞落其他住戶的信箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb816699515cfdc84f5e57cfe39d387678b4fe11","tid":1391703,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:17:59.000Z","msg":"我要贏呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaf33d5cd913099426722857a74c4104dccb8b2","tid":1391703,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8xXaq9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8xXaq9A.png&h=855876fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2db376a09b8047e4ba85d91af09d85f2d19505b","tid":1391703,"uid":274336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHO8Xgp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHO8Xgp.jpg&h=1e39aeda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8545c3250a4738c8917893938aa967aaa13aad4","tid":1391703,"uid":268537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"香港人咁實際一定係利字當頭，民主呢D虛無飄渺又長遠先見效嘅野唔會吸引到佢，如果整幾件港版韓國瑜大叫香港要發達，用短期利益引誘可唔可以吸引到藍絲支持甚至騎劫民意呢"}]}